{
    "title": "Estrada do Sol",
    "artist": "Tom Jobim",
    "composer": "Tom Jobim / Dolores Duran",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É de manhã</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Vem o sol, mas os pingos da chuva</span>\n          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que ontem caiu</span>\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ainda estão a brilhar</span>\n                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7+\">C7+</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ainda estão a dançar</span>\n          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7+\">C7+</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Ao vento alegre que me traz essa canção</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Fm7\">Fm7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb7\">Bb7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Ebm7\">Ebm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Quero que você me dê a mão</span>\n       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Ab7\">Ab7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que eu vou sair por ai</span>\n       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Sem pensar no que foi que sonhei</span>\n                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que chorei, que sofri</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Pois a nossa manhã</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7+\">C7+</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Já me fez esquecer</span>\n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em7\">Em7</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7+\">C7+</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Me dê a mão vamos sair pra ver o sol</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O sol</span>\n",
